                                            <br><em>U.S. News &amp; World Report&rsquo;s Best Colleges 2014 Edition</em> has once again named NJIT to the top tier of national universities for its range of undergraduate majors and master's and doctoral degrees. This year, NJIT was ranked 150th out of the 200+ institutions earning the distinction of top national universities.&nbsp; NJIT also ranked 6th in the nation for ethnic diversity.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.njit.edu/news/2013/2013-283.php" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.njit.edu/features/uicomponents/images/next.gif" border="0"></a>
